title: Best open source alternative to iLovePDF? : r/opensource - Reddit
snippet: I need an open-source application that can do PDF operations just like iLovePDF does. It needs to work in a self-hosted server for privacy policies, or (ideally) be an offline desktop application. The most necessary feature is "Split PDF" (convert a multi-page PDF into several single-page PDF).
